{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 4,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 453.976,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.437,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I spake unto my brethren, saying:",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.617,
      "end": 6.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Let us go up again unto Jerusalem,",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 6.212,
      "end": 7.884,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and let us be faithful",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.064,
      "end": 10.247,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in keeping the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 10.427,
      "end": 13.353,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold he is mightier than all the earth,",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 13.533,
      "end": 16.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then why not mightier than Laban and his fifty,",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 16.685,
      "end": 18.821,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, or even than his tens of thousands?",
      "verse": "4:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 19.501,
      "end": 21.405,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore let us go up;",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 21.585,
      "end": 23.768,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "let us be strong like unto Moses;",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 23.948,
      "end": 27.431,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he truly spake unto the waters of the Red Sea",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 27.611,
      "end": 29.561,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they divided hither and thither,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 29.741,
      "end": 31.691,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and our fathers came through,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 31.871,
      "end": 33.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "out of captivity,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 33.676,
      "end": 35.209,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "on dry ground,",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 35.389,
      "end": 37.757,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the armies of Pharaoh did follow",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 37.937,
      "end": 40.77,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and were drowned in the waters of the Red Sea.",
      "verse": "4:2",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 41.45,
      "end": 43.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now behold ye know that this is true;",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 43.58,
      "end": 47.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye also know that an angel hath spoken unto you;",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 47.289,
      "end": 48.868,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore can ye doubt?",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 49.048,
      "end": 50.348,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Let us go up;",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 50.528,
      "end": 52.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord is able to deliver us,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 52.891,
      "end": 54.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even as our fathers,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 54.65,
      "end": 56.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to destroy Laban,",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 56.455,
      "end": 57.895,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even as the Egyptians.",
      "verse": "4:3",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 58.575,
      "end": 61.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now when I had spoken these words, they were yet wroth,",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 62.006,
      "end": 64.142,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did still continue to murmur;",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 64.322,
      "end": 66.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless they did follow me up",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 66.731,
      "end": 69.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until we came without the walls of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "4:4",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 69.965,
      "end": 71.73,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it was by night;",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 71.91,
      "end": 75.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I caused that they should hide themselves without the walls.",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 75.991,
      "end": 78.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had hid themselves,",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 78.354,
      "end": 80.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I, Nephi, crept into the city",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 80.763,
      "end": 83.457,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and went forth towards the house of Laban.",
      "verse": "4:5",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 84.137,
      "end": 86.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I was led by the Spirit,",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 86.36,
      "end": 89.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "not knowing beforehand the things which I should do.",
      "verse": "4:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 90.105,
      "end": 92.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless I went forth,",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 92.235,
      "end": 95.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as I came near unto the house of Laban",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 95.387,
      "end": 96.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld a man,",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 97.1,
      "end": 99.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he had fallen to the earth before me,",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 99.788,
      "end": 101.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he was drunken with wine.",
      "verse": "4:7",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 102.511,
      "end": 105.855,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And when I came to him I found that it was Laban.",
      "verse": "4:8",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 106.535,
      "end": 108.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I beheld his sword,",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 108.433,
      "end": 111.034,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I drew it forth from the sheath thereof;",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 111.214,
      "end": 113.908,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the hilt thereof was of pure gold,",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 114.088,
      "end": 117.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the workmanship thereof was exceedingly fine,",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 117.379,
      "end": 119.608,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw that the blade thereof",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 119.788,
      "end": 122.064,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "was of the most precious steel.",
      "verse": "4:9",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 122.744,
      "end": 126.273,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I was constrained by the Spirit",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 126.453,
      "end": 128.078,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should kill Laban;",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 128.258,
      "end": 130.116,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but I said in my heart:",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 130.296,
      "end": 133.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Never at any time have I shed the blood of man.",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 133.309,
      "end": 136.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I shrunk and would that I might not slay him.",
      "verse": "4:10",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 137.379,
      "end": 139.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Spirit said unto me again:",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 139.835,
      "end": 142.854,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the Lord hath delivered him into thy hands.",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 143.034,
      "end": 147.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and I also knew that he had sought to take away mine own life;",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 147.626,
      "end": 151.62,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, and he would not hearken unto the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 151.8,
      "end": 154.168,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he also had taken away our property.",
      "verse": "4:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 154.848,
      "end": 158.145,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the Spirit said unto me again:",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 158.325,
      "end": 159.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Slay him,",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 159.48,
      "end": 162.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the Lord hath delivered him into thy hands;",
      "verse": "4:12",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 162.854,
      "end": 164.897,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold the Lord slayeth the wicked",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 165.077,
      "end": 167.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to bring forth his righteous purposes.",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 167.765,
      "end": 170.087,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "It is better that one man should perish",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 170.267,
      "end": 173.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "than that a nation should dwindle and perish in unbelief.",
      "verse": "4:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 174.151,
      "end": 176.798,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, when I, Nephi, had heard these words,",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 176.978,
      "end": 179.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I remembered the words of the Lord",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 179.526,
      "end": 182.637,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake unto me in the wilderness, saying that:",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 182.817,
      "end": 185.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Inasmuch as thy seed shall keep my commandments,",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 186.155,
      "end": 188.663,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall prosper in the land of promise.",
      "verse": "4:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 189.343,
      "end": 191.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and I also thought",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 191.288,
      "end": 194.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they could not keep the commandments of the Lord",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 194.208,
      "end": 196.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the law of Moses,",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 196.431,
      "end": 198.335,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save they should have the law.",
      "verse": "4:15",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 199.015,
      "end": 203.102,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also knew that the law was engraven upon the plates of brass.",
      "verse": "4:16",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 203.782,
      "end": 207.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And again, I knew that the Lord had delivered Laban",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 207.306,
      "end": 209.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into my hands for this cause\u2014",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 209.436,
      "end": 211.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I might obtain the records",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 211.892,
      "end": 213.657,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to his commandments.",
      "verse": "4:17",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 214.337,
      "end": 217.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore I did obey the voice of the Spirit,",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 217.396,
      "end": 219.997,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and took Laban by the hair of the head,",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 220.177,
      "end": 222.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I smote off his head with his own sword.",
      "verse": "4:18",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 223.318,
      "end": 226.522,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I had smitten off his head with his own sword,",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 226.702,
      "end": 230.464,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I took the garments of Laban and put them upon mine own body;",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 230.644,
      "end": 232.223,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even every whit;",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 232.403,
      "end": 235.236,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did gird on his armor about my loins.",
      "verse": "4:19",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 235.916,
      "end": 237.634,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I had done this,",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 237.814,
      "end": 240.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I went forth unto the treasury of Laban.",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 240.734,
      "end": 243.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as I went forth towards the treasury of Laban,",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 243.84,
      "end": 247.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, I saw the servant of Laban who had the keys of the treasury.",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 247.921,
      "end": 250.475,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I commanded him in the voice of Laban,",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 250.655,
      "end": 253.395,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should go with me into the treasury.",
      "verse": "4:20",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 254.075,
      "end": 257.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he supposed me to be his master, Laban,",
      "verse": "4:21",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 257.32,
      "end": 259.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he beheld the garments",
      "verse": "4:21",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 259.497,
      "end": 262.051,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also the sword girded about my loins.",
      "verse": "4:21",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 262.731,
      "end": 266.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake unto me concerning the elders of the Jews,",
      "verse": "4:22",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 266.301,
      "end": 268.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he knowing that his master, Laban,",
      "verse": "4:22",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 268.803,
      "end": 271.218,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "had been out by night among them.",
      "verse": "4:22",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 271.898,
      "end": 274.824,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I spake unto him as if it had been Laban.",
      "verse": "4:23",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 275.504,
      "end": 277.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also spake unto him",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 277.727,
      "end": 279.91,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I should carry the engravings,",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 280.09,
      "end": 282.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 282.685,
      "end": 284.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to my elder brethren,",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 284.49,
      "end": 286.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were without the walls.",
      "verse": "4:24",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 286.935,
      "end": 289.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also bade him that he should follow me.",
      "verse": "4:25",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 290.03,
      "end": 293.699,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he, supposing that I spake of the brethren of the church,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 293.879,
      "end": 297.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that I was truly that Laban whom I had slain,",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 297.31,
      "end": 299.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore he did follow me.",
      "verse": "4:26",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 299.708,
      "end": 303.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he spake unto me many times concerning the elders of the Jews,",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 304.068,
      "end": 306.344,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as I went forth unto my brethren,",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 306.524,
      "end": 308.289,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who were without the walls.",
      "verse": "4:27",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 308.969,
      "end": 311.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when Laman saw me",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 311.657,
      "end": 313.654,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he was exceedingly frightened,",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 313.834,
      "end": 315.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also Lemuel and Sam.",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 315.779,
      "end": 318.287,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they fled from before my presence;",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 318.467,
      "end": 320.557,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they supposed it was Laban,",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 320.737,
      "end": 322.502,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that he had slain me",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 322.682,
      "end": 325.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had sought to take away their lives also.",
      "verse": "4:28",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 326.148,
      "end": 328.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I called after them,",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 329.068,
      "end": 330.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did hear me;",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 330.92,
      "end": 334.124,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore they did cease to flee from my presence.",
      "verse": "4:29",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 334.804,
      "end": 339.355,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when the servant of Laban beheld my brethren",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 339.535,
      "end": 341.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he began to tremble,",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 341.294,
      "end": 343.662,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and was about to flee from before me",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 343.842,
      "end": 346.118,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and return to the city of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "4:30",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 346.798,
      "end": 350.188,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, being a man large in stature,",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 350.368,
      "end": 353.572,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also having received much strength of the Lord,",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 353.752,
      "end": 356.91,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "therefore I did seize upon the servant of Laban,",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 357.09,
      "end": 358.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and held him,",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 358.431,
      "end": 359.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should not flee.",
      "verse": "4:31",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 360.597,
      "end": 363.058,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I spake with him,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 363.238,
      "end": 365.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if he would hearken unto my words,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 365.786,
      "end": 367.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as the Lord liveth,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 367.452,
      "end": 368.845,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and as I live,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 369.025,
      "end": 372.276,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even so that if he would hearken unto our words,",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 372.456,
      "end": 374.081,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we would spare his life.",
      "verse": "4:32",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 374.761,
      "end": 376.386,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I spake unto him,",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 376.566,
      "end": 377.959,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even with an oath,",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 378.139,
      "end": 379.857,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he need not fear;",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 380.037,
      "end": 382.87,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he should be a free man like unto us",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 383.05,
      "end": 386.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if he would go down in the wilderness with us.",
      "verse": "4:33",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 386.795,
      "end": 389.256,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also spake unto him, saying:",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 389.436,
      "end": 392.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Surely the Lord hath commanded us to do this thing;",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 392.727,
      "end": 394.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall we not be diligent",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 394.765,
      "end": 396.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in keeping the commandments of the Lord?",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 397.174,
      "end": 399.682,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Therefore, if thou wilt go down",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 399.862,
      "end": 402.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into the wilderness to my father",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 402.596,
      "end": 404.593,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "thou shalt have place with us.",
      "verse": "4:34",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 405.273,
      "end": 409.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that Zoram did take courage at the words which I spake.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 409.633,
      "end": 411.909,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now Zoram was the name of the servant;",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 412.089,
      "end": 414.504,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he promised that he would go down",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 414.684,
      "end": 417.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "into the wilderness unto our father.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 417.465,
      "end": 420.112,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and he also made an oath unto us",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 420.292,
      "end": 423.45,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would tarry with us from that time forth.",
      "verse": "4:35",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 424.13,
      "end": 428.031,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now we were desirous that he should tarry with us for this cause,",
      "verse": "4:36",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 428.211,
      "end": 432.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Jews might not know concerning our flight into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "4:36",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 433.174,
      "end": 435.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest they should pursue us and destroy us.",
      "verse": "4:36",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 436.408,
      "end": 439.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that when Zoram had made an oath unto us,",
      "verse": "4:37",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 440.117,
      "end": 442.718,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "our fears did cease concerning him.",
      "verse": "4:37",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 443.398,
      "end": 446.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we took the plates of brass",
      "verse": "4:38",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 446.457,
      "end": 448.315,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the servant of Laban,",
      "verse": "4:38",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 448.495,
      "end": 450.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and departed into the wilderness,",
      "verse": "4:38",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 450.951,
      "end": 453.319,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and journeyed unto the tent of our father.",
      "verse": "4:38",
      "lineIndex": 166
    }
  ]
}